__e: I hold you in high regard, Grace, you know this... your strength and your intelligence and your beauty,
They were threatened by my intelligence and too stupid to know that's why they hated me.
Here we all are, back on Earth, with nothing but our wit and our will to save the world.
My only assets are my wits, and as the man who just lost 5,000 pesos of his ship's own money, they are ill-valued at the moment.
Intelligence is not a disease that you have to protect him from.
